ing: 1 (3 pound) butternut squash - peeled, seeded, and cut into cubes
des: "I couldn't find a good recipe for slow cooked squash online, so I just made one myself!"
ins:
Combine butternut squash and apple juice in a slow cooker. Whisk butter, brown sugar, and cinnamon together in a bowl; drizzle over butternut squash.
Cook on Low for 6 to 8 hours.
